Backend:

Favorites & Watchlist:

POST /api/user/favorites

POST /api/user/watchlist


Ratings & Reviews:

POST /api/reviews

Allow users to rate and leave a comment


User Profile:

GET /api/user/profile

PUT /api/user/profile



Frontend:

Allow adding/removing favorites

Star rating input

Review text input

User dashboard to manage profile, watchlist, ratings



